= The Commission and Sponsorship Plan

This project began as a way to build memories with "#ruby[らいは][礼羽]みや".

Each month I will post a small treat by Kamiyoru on the platforms below, including *SD illustrations* and *emotes*~

By supporting me on the following platforms, you can receive *keychains* and *shikishi* made from these works:
- Subscribe to "A cup of cappuccino" or "Support my OC" on Afdian or Unifans during that month.
- Or support "Buy me a coffee" on Afdian with at least 2 USD dollars during that month.

The received sponsorships are mainly used for commissions!

Since I already have supporters from all over the world, and some of them may not be interested in my gifts. To avoid bothering them, please send me a direct message during the same month after supporting me and let me know which small gift you want.

Only one small gift can be claimed each month. The current gifts (planned) are:

- April 2026: a QQ Candy keychain of "怡子曰曰".
- May 2026: a shikishi art board of "阿黄".
- June 2026: a QQ Candy keychain of "月见".

Because the gifts are custom-made by manufacturers, delivery may be delayed.

Supporters overseas, or in western China, may need to discuss and pay additional shipping costs.

